<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Welcome</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2563eb;">Welcome to Digital Directory!</h1>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>Thank you for registering. Please verify your email address to get started.</p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      Verify Email Address
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
